---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Soul Lab Recovery — Sauna & Ice Bath Services in Townsville"
  description="Premium sauna and ice bath recovery services. Single sessions, 5-session packages, or unlimited monthly membership. Available for gym members and the public."
>
  <Nav />

  <!-- TOP BUTTONS (Before Nav) -->
  <div class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-40 bg-white">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-0">
      <a
        href="https://slg.gymdesk.com/signup"
        class="bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-4 text-center transition-colors"
      >
        Sign Up
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://slg.gymdesk.com/login"
        class="bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-4 text-center transition-colors"
      >
        Login
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-40 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-green-50 to-white">
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center py-20">
      <div class="inline-block bg-pink-100 border border-pink-300 text-pink-700 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6">
        Recovery Services • Soul Lab Gym
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-4">
        Recover Faster.<br>
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-green-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Feel Better.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-800 font-medium mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Premium sauna and ice bath recovery services in Townsville. Optimize your training, boost immunity, and reset your mind.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="https://slg.gymdesk.com/login"
          class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-green-400 hover:from-pink-600 hover:to-green-500 text-white font-bold text-base px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-all shadow-lg"
        >
          Book Your First Session
        </a>
        <a
          href="#benefits"
          class="border-2 border-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 text-gray-900 font-bold text-base px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors"
        >
          Learn More
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT SECTION -->
  <section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">What is Sauna & Ice Bath Recovery?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Sauna and ice bath therapy are time-tested recovery modalities used by elite athletes, fighters, and wellness-focused individuals. The contrast between heat and cold triggers powerful adaptations in your nervous system, circulation, and recovery capacity.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          At Soul Lab Recovery, we provide a controlled, safe environment to experience these benefits with expert guidance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-green-200 hover:border-pink-300 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-green-700">
            ✓
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Faster Recovery</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Reduce muscle soreness, accelerate healing, and bounce back from intense training sessions in half the time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-pink-200 hover:border-green-300 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-pink-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-pink-700">
            ✓
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Mental Clarity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Reset your nervous system, reduce stress, and experience the mental edge that comes from deliberate recovery.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-green-200 hover:border-pink-300 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-blue-700">
            ✓
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Immune Boost</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Strengthen immune resilience through heat shock proteins and improved circulation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BENEFITS SECTION -->
  <section id="benefits" class="py-20 bg-white border-t border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Why Athletes & Wellness Enthusiasts Choose Soul Lab Recovery</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-green-400 text-white">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Professional-Grade Equipment</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">Commercial-quality sauna and ice bath facilities designed for serious recovery.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-green-400 text-white">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Expert Guidance</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">Our team understands the science and will help you get the most from each session.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-green-400 text-white">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Flexible Membership</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">Drop-in sessions or commitment-free packages. Choose what works for you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-green-400 text-white">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Community Focused</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">Part of the Soul Lab family. Recover alongside serious athletes and wellness enthusiasts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING SECTION -->
  <section id="pricing" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-green-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">Pricing Plans</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">Choose the plan that fits your recovery goals.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Single Session -->
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-pink-300 transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Single Session</h3>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl font-black text-pink-600">$35</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 ml-2">per session</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Sauna + Ice Bath combo</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>30-minute session</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Expert guidance included</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://slg.gymdesk.com/login" class="block text-center bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-800 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-full transition-colors">
            Book Now
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- 5-Session Package -->
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-green-400 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-green-400 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold">
            20% OFF
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">5-Session Package</h3>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl font-black text-pink-600">$150</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 ml-2">$30 per session</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>5 x 30-minute sessions</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Save $25 vs single sessions</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Valid for 3 months</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Expert guidance included</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://slg.gymdesk.com/login" class="block text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-green-400 hover:from-pink-600 hover:to-green-500 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-full transition-all shadow-lg">
            Get Package
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Monthly Unlimited -->
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-pink-300 transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Monthly Unlimited</h3>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl font-black text-pink-600">$89</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 ml-2">per month</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Unlimited monthly access</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>30-minute sessions</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Best value for regulars</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-pink-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              <span>Expert guidance included</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://slg.gymdesk.com/login" class="block text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-green-400 hover:from-pink-600 hover:to-green-500 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-full transition-all shadow-lg">
            Subscribe
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-pink-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
          <strong>Soul Lab Gym Members:</strong> Get 15% off all packages. Ask at the front desk for your recovery discount code.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer group hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">
            How hot is the sauna?
            <span class="text-pink-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">Our sauna maintains a temperature of 160-180°F (70-82°C), which is ideal for health benefits while remaining comfortable for most people. You can adjust your experience by spending more or less time inside.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer group hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">
            Is ice bath exposure dangerous?
            <span class="text-pink-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">No. Our ice bath temperatures (50-60°F / 10-15°C) are safe for most people when done properly. We guide you through gradual exposure and breathing techniques to make it comfortable. Always consult your doctor if you have cardiovascular concerns.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer group hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">
            I've never done this before. Is it for beginners?
            <span class="text-pink-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">Absolutely. Every session is guided by our team. Beginners start with shorter durations and warmer water, and we teach proper breathing and mental techniques to make it enjoyable. No experience needed.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer group hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">
            How long does a typical session take?
            <span class="text-pink-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">Plan for 45-60 minutes total. This includes 15-20 minutes in the sauna, 2-3 minutes in the ice bath, and 15 minutes of rest/integration afterward. We keep you moving safely between the two.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer group hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">
            Can I do this after my gym workout?
            <span class="text-pink-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">Yes. In fact, recovery sessions are best done 30 minutes to 2 hours post-workout. This is when your body is primed to benefit from the temperature contrast and healing adaptations.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer group hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">
            Are there any health conditions that would prevent me from using it?
            <span class="text-pink-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">Pregnancy, severe cardiovascular disease, and some medications require medical clearance. We'll ask about your health history during your first session. When in doubt, chat with your doctor first.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white border-t-2 border-pink-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">What Athletes & Members Say</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">Real feedback from people using Soul Lab Recovery.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-green-200 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="flex gap-0.5 mb-4">
            <span class="text-pink-500 text-lg">★</span>
            <span class="text-pink-500 text-lg">★</span>
            <span class="text-pink-500 text-lg">★</span>
            <span class="text-pink-500 text-lg">★</span>
            <span class="text-pink-500 text-lg">★</span>
          </div>
