            <span class="text-pink-500 text-lg">★</span>
            <span class="text-pink-500 text-lg">★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">
            "I feel mentally sharper after each session. It's become part of my daily routine."
          </p>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">— [Name], Member</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-green-200 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="flex gap-0.5 mb-4">
            <span class="text-pink-500 text-lg">★</span>
            <span class="text-pink-500 text-lg">★</span>
            <span class="text-pink-500 text-lg">★</span>
            <span class="text-pink-500 text-lg">★</span>
            <span class="text-pink-500 text-lg">★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">
            "The team makes you feel safe and guided through the whole experience. Worth every dollar."
          </p>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">— [Name], Gym Member</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Video Testimonials -->
      <div class="mt-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-pink-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">See Recovery in Action</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Watch members share their recovery experience and results on our YouTube channel.
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMGyz96tdBUgD-RG6SyEDRg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-green-400 hover:from-pink-600 hover:to-green-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full transition-all shadow-lg">
          Watch Videos on YouTube
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA SECTION -->
  <section id="book" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-green-400">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-white mb-4">Ready to Recover Better?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8">
        Book your first session today. Expert guidance included.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="https://slg.gymdesk.com/login" class="inline-block bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 text-pink-600 font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full transition-colors shadow-lg">
          Login to Book
        </a>
        <a href="https://slg.gymdesk.com/signup" class="inline-block border-2 border-white hover:bg-white/10 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full transition-colors">
